; CHECK-LSC: call <1 x double> @llvm.vc.internal.lsc.load.bti.v1f64.v1i1.v2i8.i32(<1 x i1> <i1 true>, i8 2, i8 4, i8 1, <2 x i8> zeroinitializer, i32 255, i32 %{{[a-zA-Z0-9.]+}}, i16 1, i32 0, <1 x double> undef)
